(18452, 'Epirovastin 20 mg 14 f.c. tab', 'ابيروفاستين 20مجم 14 قرص', '28.5', '76', 'Rosuvastatin', 'Eipico', 'Tab', 'أقراص', 'دواء خافض لدهون الدم', 'Antihyperlipidemic.statins', '20 mg', 'The FDA monograph states that rosuvastatin is indicated as an adjunct to diet in the treatment of triglyceridemia, Primary Dysbetalipoproteinemia (Type III Hyperlipoproteinemia), and Homozygous Familial Hypercholesterolemia.[F4649]
